## 七、MySQL 查询规范

### 4.1 新模块优先使用 GenericService + QLInfo

**推荐写法**：使用 `GenericService` + `QLInfo` + `andClause`

```java
@Autowired
private GenericService genericService;

// 分页查询
public PageInfo<MyEntity> pageQuery(MyQueryReq req) {
    QLInfo<MyEntity> qlInfo = QLInfo.buildQl(
        " from " + MyEntity.class.getName() + " a ",
        MyEntity.class
    );

    // 动态条件：第一个参数为 true 时添加条件
    qlInfo.andClause(req.getId() != null, " a.id = ?", req.getId());
    qlInfo.andClause(StringUtils.isNotBlank(req.getName()), " a.name like ?", "%" + req.getName() + "%");
    qlInfo.andClause(req.getStartTime() != null, " a.createTime >= ?", req.getStartTime());
    qlInfo.andClause(req.getEndTime() != null, " a.createTime <= ?", req.getEndTime());

    // 分页排序
    qlInfo.setSort("a.createTime");
    qlInfo.setDir("DESC");
    qlInfo.setPageNoAndPageSize(req.getCurrent(), req.getSize());

    // 查询
    PageInfo<MyEntity> pageResult = genericService.searchByQl(qlInfo, true);
    return pageResult.convertData(entity -> {
        MyDTO dto = new MyDTO();
        ModelUtil.copy(entity, dto);
        return dto;
    });
}
```

### 4.2 条件查询 `andClause` 用法

```java
// 基础用法：条件为 true 时添加
qlInfo.andClause(condition, " a.field = ?", value);

// 字符串模糊查询
qlInfo.andClause(StringUtils.isNotBlank(name), " a.name like ?", "%" + name + "%");

// 日期范围查询
qlInfo.andClause(startTime != null, " a.createTime >= ?", startTime);
qlInfo.andClause(endTime != null, " a.createTime <= ?", endTime);

// IN 查询
qlInfo.andClause(!CollectionUtils.isEmpty(statusList),
    " a.status in (" + String.join(",", Collections.nCopies(statusList.size(), "?")) + ")",
    statusList.toArray());
```

### 4.3 权限控制 `setDisablePermissionFilter`

```java
// 禁用权限过滤，所有人查得到
qlInfo.setDisablePermissionFilter(true);

// 注意：实体需要映射用户字段（createBy）
// 系统会根据表的用户ID自动匹配数据权限
```

### 4.4 复杂多表查询 — 使用块字符串写法

**适用场景**：多表关联查询，且实体没有 JPA 映射关系

```java
// 临时处理：后续可抽取数据到宽表
String sql = """
    select t.id as workflowTaskId,
           i.task_name as taskName,
           p.comment as nodeName,
           i.request_id as requestId,
           i.id as instanceId,
           t.status as status,
           i.status as instanceStatus,
           i.result as errorMessage,
           DATE_FORMAT(t.create_time, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS createTime,
           DATE_FORMAT(t.update_time, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS updateTime
    from llm_workflow_task t
         join llm_agent_instance i on t.process_instance_id = i.id and i.instance_source = ?
         join llm_agent_plan p on p.id = t.node_id
    where i.status in (?,?)
    """;

QLInfo<TaskAbnormalDTO> qlInfo = QLInfo.buildSqlInfo(sql, TaskAbnormalDTO.class,
    LLMAgentInstance.INSTANCE_SOURCE_WORKFLOW,
    ITaskStatus.STATUS_TIMEOUT_EXIT,
    ITaskStatus.STATUS_FAILED);

qlInfo.setSort("t.create_time");
qlInfo.setDir("ASC");
```

### 4.5 不使用 JPA Repository 的场景

- 新模块没有定义 `@Repository` 接口
- 需要动态条件查询
- 需要自定义 SQL（多表关联、聚合等）
- 需要禁用权限过滤

